{"tid":2488531,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"outriders真係超爛game","createTime":"2021-04-14T09:56:36.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-14T11:44:28.000Z","uid":44898,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e7d07b3637e2ede6b555907eaa62389794f1ab79","tid":2488531,"uid":44898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T09:56:36.000Z","msg":"玩左4日，重爛過聖歌剛剛出果時<br />\n睇怕隻game又係半成品<br />\n無得改無得救<br />\n<br />\n畫面屎<br />\n介面屎<br />\n操控屎<br />\n連接屎<br />\n手感爛<br />\n單機玩要連線屎<br />\n3人連機設計超屎<br />\n<br />\n今時今日竟然無得主動隨機連線<br />\n你隨機搵人，又無得選關卡<br />\n<br />\n狂彈機，加埋hold機無得登入<br />\n玩玩下lag,d制hold死無反應<br />\nbug 多撚到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n依隻真係2021暫時最爛，<br />\n重賣4百幾，連幾年前<br />\ndistiny 都不如<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b19e84a201ea6251d256d1374643990c7fb7e69","tid":2488531,"uid":278184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T11:15:42.000Z","msg":"係咪同果陣AMTHEM差唔多"},{"pid":"995bd3d192eb1fadac3940f9fc52c44b28dd048f","tid":2488531,"uid":44898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T11:42:33.000Z","msg":"係屎過聖歌好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你話死未<br />\n個遊戲介面同聯線，<br />\n直頭唔掂，我覺得個聯機<br />\n係後期監粗加落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n聖歌打關卡，都刷得好好玩<br />\n<br />\n依隻game,實在太多問題<br />\n同埋地圖方向任務好亂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最想講，隻game畫面，<br />\n反應係ps3水平，<br />\n你點調個描準靈敏度<br />\n都係較唔到好操作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f1048fe12b1e7c66d948cbf84ed14a3dcef7add","tid":2488531,"uid":308887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T11:44:28.000Z","msg":"好在冇中伏<img